edu.ucla.sspace.graph.isomorphism
Interface IsomorphismTester

All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractIsomorphismTester, TypedVF2IsomorphismTester, VF2IsomorphismTester
public interface IsomorphismTester

An interface for algorithms that detect whether two graphs are isomorphic. Implementations are open to define any further refinements beyond structural isomorphism, which may include:

  • node types
  • edge types
  • edge weights
  • edge directions
.

Method Summary
